    "Google/Gemma-7B.",
    "Gemma models are a series of state-of-the-art, lightweight language models developed by Google, utilizing the same innovative technology as the Gemini models.",
    "These text-totext, decoder-only models are available in English, featuring open weights and both pre-trained and instruction-tuned variants.",
    "Designed for versatility, Gemma models excel in various text generation tasks like question answering, summarization, and reasoning, with their compact size allowing deployment in resource-limited settings, thus broadening access to cutting-edge AI technology.",
    "Refer to (Team et al., 2024) for details."
